track_notes:
MONVISO The Stone King the most beautiful peak of Piemonte.
Classif. A  You need alpinistic training and materials ( helmet, crampons, rope, etc ).
1° day 700 m to rifugio Quintino Sella ( founder of CAI Club Alpino Italiano )
2° day wake up at 4:30 back to the car at 21:30 = 17 hours total ascent 2100 m 

JOINT Activation I1WKN Beppe, IZ1BPN Stefano, IK1RAC Vittorio, IW2NHE Alberto.
track_title: The sharp profile of Stone KING
